**Core Responsibilities:**

- Maintain customer-first mentality
- Service, nurture, and grow your portfolio
- Educate customers on best practices within their product mix
- Manage the full life cycle of campaigns, including onboarding, growing, and retaining
- Manage a large volume of inbound/outbound calls daily

**Experience Required:**

- Previous experience in account management in a high volume phone based role
- Ability to work autonomously with non-face-to-face support
- Familiarity with Salesforce
- Exposure to online marketing or advertising
- Capability to not only service customers but continue their growth
- Aptitude in utilizing data within your recommendations

**Keywords:**

- Account Manager
- Customer-first mentality
- Service & Nurture portfolio
- Customer Education
- Campaign Management
- Onboarding, Growing, Retaining
- Volume of calls
- Autonomy
- Salesforce
- Online Marketing
- Advertising
- Customer Growth
- Data utilization.